      ***                    M A I N L I N E S                      ***
      *****************************************************************
      *
      ***  Test Modules Flag
      *
     C                     EXSR #MODL                      TEST MODULES
      *
      ***  Check Rundate and Activation Date
      *
     C                     EXSR #DATE                      RUN DATE
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *  #MODL  : Test modules                                        *
      *  Called by :                                                  *
      *  Calls     : Mainlines                                        *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           #MODL     BEGSR
      *
      ***  Reset every Module to NO
      *
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILCOB
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILGLMO
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILREMO
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILDLMO
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILLEMO
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILSEMO
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILFTMO
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILFFMO
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILPMMO
      *
      ***  Retrieved module for which IBLC is Activated
      ***  General ledger
      *
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN30
     C                     TESTB'0'       CHR1           30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       ILGLMO
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ***  Retail
      *
     C                     TESTB'1'       CHR1           30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       ILREMO
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ***  Dealing
      *
     C                     TESTB'2'       CHR1           30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       ILDLMO
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ***  Customer lending
      *
     C                     TESTB'3'       CHR1           30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       ILLEMO
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ***  Securities trading
      *
     C                     TESTB'4'       CHR1           30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       ILSEMO
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ***  Funds transfers
      *
     C                     TESTB'5'       CHR1           30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       ILFTMO
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ***  Futures and options
      *
     C                     TESTB'6'       CHR1           30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       ILFFMO
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ***  Portfolio management
      *
     C                     TESTB'1'       CHR2           30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       ILPMMO
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ***  Run IBLC (C.O.B. components)
      ***  If Activation Date is REACHED and Asked in ICD.
      *
     C                     TESTB'7'       CHR2           30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ *ON
     C           ICACTD    ANDLEBJRDNB                     Activ. date Reached
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       ILCOB
     C                     ELSE
      *
      ***  Ensure nothing will start
      *
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILCOB
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILGLMO
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILREMO
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILDLMO
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILLEMO
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILSEMO
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILFTMO
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILFFMO
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ILPMMO
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *  #DATE  : Routine to setup date of accounting                 *
      *  ------                                                       *
      *  Called by : Mainlines                                        *
      *  Calls     :                                                  *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           #DATE     BEGSR
      *
      ***  Set up DAY
      *
     C                     Z-ADDWWBJD     WWBJDP  20       DAY
     C                     Z-ADDWWBJDP    ILDADD           DAY
      *
      ***  Set up MONTH
      *
     C                     Z-ADD1         X       20       X : INDEX
     C           WWBJM     LOKUPZMNM,X                   2626 : EQUAL
     C           *IN26     IFEQ *ON
     C                     Z-ADDX         ILDAMM           MONTH
     C                     END
      *
      ***  Set up YEAR
      *
     C                     Z-ADDWWBJY     ILDAYY           YEAR
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *  *INZSR - Initial Subroutine - Started automatically          *
      *  Called by : at Pgm start                                     *
      *  Calls     :                                                  *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           *INZSR    BEGSR
      *
      ***  Copyrigth
      *
     C                     MOVEACPY@      CPY2@  80
      *
      ***  Prepare LDA:
      *
     C                     MOVEL'IL0600'  DBPGM
      *
      ***  Installation control data
      *
     C                     READ SDBANKL1                 99
      *
      ***  handle database error
      *
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *ON
     C                     Z-ADD1         DBASE            ****************
