     C                     MOVEL'*FIRST'  DBKEY     P      ****************
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ***  IBLC installation control
      *
     C           1         SETLLILICDRPD
     C                     READ ILICDRPD                 99
      *
      ***  handle database error
      *
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *ON
     C                     Z-ADD2         DBASE            ****************
