     C                     MOVEL'*FIRST'  DBKEY     P      ****************
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *  *PSSR  : Routine to handle Leave when databse error occurs   *
      *  ------                                                       *
      *  Called by : *INZSR                                          *
      *  Calls     :                                                  *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           *PSSR     BEGSR
